original_title: Kyle Kinane: Trampoline In A Ditch
overview: Offering up a hearty dose of Kyle Kinane’s critically-acclaimed brand of observational comedy, the live video recording behind Kinane’s fifth stand-up album, ‘Trampoline In A Ditch’ was recorded in Madison, WI in March 2019.
title: Kyle Kinane: Trampoline In A Ditch
